text-indent.  a=dmeehan\n\nDon't apply text-indent to the outer input frame, since all the inner\nframes also apply it. This gets the behavior from before my patch and is\nconsistent with other browsers as well.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D296252\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D296729\n", "files": ["layout/generic/nsLineLayout.cpp", "testing/web-platform/tests/html/rendering/replaced-elements/attributes-for-embedded-content-and-images/input-text-indent-ref.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/html/rendering/replaced-elements/attributes-for-embedded-content-and-images/input-text-indent.html"], "git_node": "4e0e1888a6ebd36ba75027a8964afa86efe5a2cf", "git_parents": ["92a1f0e64ac82bd9362fa82cb2ca2d7eee1900e3"], "node": "f0b90405345389ff0a71cc0ba75dc9bf5970b2be", "parents": ["1a1e3c593d14537c38c0795b34220949c1c67b0a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1777325220, "git_changesets": ["4e0e1888a6ebd36ba75027a8964afa86efe5a2cf"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "25970": {"changesets": [{"author": "John M. Schanck \u003cjschanck@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2033147 - set getClientCapabilities extension:largeBlob flag to true on Android.  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D295107\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D296737\n", "files": ["dom/webauthn/PublicKeyCredential.cpp"], "git_node": "556030d97a4c0e671a9031b0be71f650db32a658", "git_parents": ["4e0e1888a6ebd36ba75027a8964afa86efe5a2cf"], "node": "3b5a0cced4f948f58bf84b12494f19d4ec1cf6dc", "parents": ["f0b90405345389ff0a71cc0ba75dc9bf5970b2be"], "tags": []}], "date": 1777325266, "git_changesets": ["556030d97a4c0e671a9031b0be71f650db32a658"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "25971": {"changesets": [{"author": "Harshit Sohaney \u003chsohaney@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2032452 - enable firefox backup on all platforms.  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision