uld\nupdate kblock state of the chrome document as well, so that the correct\nwarning is displayed.\n\nAdded web platform tests that test for this specific scenario.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D295315\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D298770\n", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp", "dom/base/Document.h", "dom/base/FullscreenChange.h", "testing/web-platform/meta/fullscreen/api/keyboard-lock-cross-origin-iframe.tentative.sub.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/tests/fullscreen/api/keyboard-lock-cross-origin-iframe.tentative.sub.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/fullscreen/api/resources/keyboard-lock-inner.sub.html"], "git_node": "4fc6fe7f325110fc3902734a6478bc407933fac2", "git_parents": ["cb5387a6af3a5cd079510e401b5e1b35079035e9"], "node": "4b9dca5503c26df50d425a6fe7efd591f0f4c377", "parents": ["86df53a6b141997d18fe42ccd890a8675d81cd63"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778160671, "git_changesets": ["4fc6fe7f325110fc3902734a6478bc407933fac2"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26226": {"changesets": [{"author": "DonalMe \u003c76789979+DonalMe@users.noreply.github.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Bump Application Services Release to 151.0.1. a=me\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/plugins/dependencies/src/main/java/ApplicationServices.kt"], "git_node": "84e74638382c7f6befa35bea2da5fba856687e8f", "git_parents": ["4fc6fe7f325110fc3902734a6478bc407933fac2"], "node": "8c8334721c3628948fd607f3173dfccedd923d5a", "parents": ["4b9dca5503c26df50d425a6fe7efd591f0f4c377"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778166933, "git_changesets": ["84e74638382c7f6befa35bea2da5fba856687e8f"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26227": {"changesets": [{"author": "Rebecca King \u003crking@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2032599 - Update unauthenticated panel UI -  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D295319\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.m