 Werth \u003cbwerth@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2034952: Remove an expensive alpha check from AppleVTDecoder.  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D298710\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299198\n", "files": ["dom/media/platforms/apple/AppleVTDecoder.cpp"], "git_node": "3ec8150f399ce480e7d5208056f15f4141c3f167", "git_parents": ["68663ad294c73d73a26074f0c6d4a850abd98be4"], "node": "0760e7fae317ebf73e7726befe914f6271aaa4b8", "parents": ["c3ae55dce09a1402b8989dc9c0cbe46257006b0e"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778181926, "git_changesets": ["3ec8150f399ce480e7d5208056f15f4141c3f167"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26230": {"changesets": [{"author": "Glenn Watson \u003cgit@chillybin.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2035734 - Align box-shadow analytical clip with rounded prim_rect  a=dmeehan\n\ncreate_quad_primitive rounds prim_rect in device space, but\nelement_offset_rel_prim and dest_rect_offset were computed against the\nun-rounded prim_rect.min. The shader reconstructs absolute positions\nfrom the rounded local_prim_rect.p0, shifting the analytical element\nclip by up to half a device pixel and producing a one-pixel seam on\ntrailing edges at fractional device coordinates.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D297513\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299212\n", "files": ["gfx/wr/webrender/src/prepare.rs", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-inset.png", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-inset.yaml", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-negative.png", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-negative.yaml", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-spread.png", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-spread.yaml", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-transform.png", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/box-shadow-fractional-transform.yaml", "gfx/wr/wrench/reftests/boxshadow/reftest.list"], "git_node": "9b6d61a89ef6b242ec2f47fea4770ace71a2a66a", "git_parents": ["3ec8150f399ce480e7d5208056f15f4141c3f167"], "node": "5ca58f1d17fb3db30da93d597122441e0ac3bc03", "parents": ["0760e7fae317ebf73e7726befe914f6271aaa4b8"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778182999, "git_changesets": ["9b6d61a89ef6b242ec2f47fea4770ace71a2a66a"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26231": {"changesets": [{"author": "ffxbld \u003cffxbld@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug, mozilla-beta repo-update remote-settings tld-suffixes mobile-experiments ct-logs -  a=dmeehan\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299222\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/raw/initial_experiments.json", "netwerk/dns/effective_tld_names.dat", "security/ct/CTKnownLogs.h", "security/manager/tools/log_list.json", "services/settings/dumps/blocklists/addons-bloomfilters.json", "services/settings/dumps/main/ai-window-prompts.json", "services/settings/dumps/main/search-config-v2.json"], "git_node": "54a70983382ac0e9de247495460e69adc4f7ae9d", "git_parents": ["9b6d61a89ef6b242ec2f47fea4770ace71a2a66a"], "node": "5ba72b3ed57c6385c91ac6d7f351f3c039b7c0e0", "parents": ["5ca58f1d17fb3db30da93d597122441e0ac3bc03"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778188144, "git_changesets": ["54a70983382ac0e9de247495460e69adc4f7ae9d"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26232": {"changesets": [{"author": "Sammy Khamis \u003cskhamis@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2035981: Fix app_menu not recording the appropiate send_tab clicked event  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D297545\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299244\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser-sync.js", "browser/base/content/test/sync/browser_sendtab_telemetry.js"], "git_node": "5c1ec4e3ef6493d44fc4a4338d80f67801d1516f", "git_par