em in the \"More Tools\"\nsection of the Application Menu is properly hidden when the Translations\nfeature becomes disabled.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299140\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299343\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_full_page_ai_feature_app_menu.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/head.js"], "git_node": "3212ea4ccc09c3c516eb877710df864943a1be74", "git_parents": ["4ff2e31c30425f7ff52ed52d62675cabf5dae327"], "node": "fefc7c884f67d6c4a73a8a391fe3ce62f25675e6", "parents": ["1cd487b24450d73778702371e00e266db29f4717"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778271607, "git_changesets": ["3212ea4ccc09c3c516eb877710df864943a1be74"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26251": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jed Davis \u003cjld@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2034713.  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D298412\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299209\n", "files": ["security/sandbox/linux/broker/SandboxBroker.cpp"], "git_node": "d16e219c8bd5d8271a93be67195ec82d51c407ba", "git_parents": ["3212ea4ccc09c3c516eb877710df864943a1be74"], "node": "18ac442ddb9155e6fa07f53c13a8743695883887", "parents": ["fefc7c884f67d6c4a73a8a391fe3ce62f25675e6"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778271648, "git_changesets": ["d16e219c8bd5d8271a93be67195ec82d51c407ba"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26252": {"changesets": [{"author": "kpatenio \u003ckpatenio@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2037568 \u2014 fix X icons for tabs enlarging after opening VPN location selector subview.  a=dmeehan\n\nStops importing global.css in locations-subview.css. Since ipprotection-locations and locations-list components render in the light DOM, they already inherit global.css from browser.xhtml. The redundant import caused close-icon.css, which is also imported via global.css, to be inserted dynamically on subview open. As a result, close-icon.css loaded after tabs.css, making the tab close button use the wrong styles.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D298910\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299424\n", "files": ["browser/components/ipprotection/content/locations-subview.css"], "git_node": "ca2de46605c3858e60129e012129e4b683b3775e", "git_parents": ["d16e219c8bd5d8271a93be67195ec82d51c407ba"], "node": "83744b67ed971f27b7ad8c6484ca0e477d2bbd59", "parents": ["18ac442ddb9155e6fa07f53c13a8743695883887"], "tags": []}, {"author": "kpatenio \u003ckpatenio@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2037671 \u2014 remove info button from locations subview.  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299002\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299427\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/appmenu-viewcache.inc.xhtml", "browser/components/ipprotection/IPProtectionPanel.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_ipprotection_locations_keyboard_navigation.js", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_ipprotection_panel.js"], "git_node": "e566a5e34f01360838b7001266769df9ca47156c", "git_parents": ["ca2de46605c3858e60129e012129e4b683b3775e"], "node": "7452797ad485cfe2f8c5722937e066e0abdc534b", "parents": ["83744b67ed971f27b7ad8c6484ca0e477d2bbd59"], "tags": []}], "date": 1778271690, "git_changesets": ["ca2de46605c3858e60129e012129e4b683b3775e", "e566a5e34f01360838b7001266769df9ca47156c"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "26253": {"changesets": [{"author": "Ed Lee \u003cedilee@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2037980 - Instrument telemetry for Smart Window \u2194 Classic Window switching and duration tracking  a=dmeehan\n\nadd new close_window with duration and tab count shared with existing open_window and classic_switch\n\nOriginal Revisi